{"tid":923782,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"同男仔一齊好似湊仔咁？","createTime":"2018-12-01T14:04:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-02T00:21:03.000Z","uid":208061,"like":15,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"425da5034de2f56b31805f69576c302ad5ca1c49","tid":923782,"uid":208061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T14:04:23.000Z","msg":"識咗個男仔，外表係自己中意嘅style，未熟之前覺得佢係少少怕羞同貪玩嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/40.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n識耐咗會有心動嘅感覺，都係差臨門一腳表白就一齊<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">但問題嚟啦！！！！</span><br />\n佢真係好似<span style=\"color: red;\">小朋友</span><br />\n同佢一齊有時好似<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">湊仔</span></span>咁<br />\n間唔中就叫我幫佢做呢樣做嗰樣，雖然我唔會次次都應承<br />\n有時好驚佢係利用我幫佢做嘢而唔係真係中意我，身邊朋友話佢係playboy<br />\n但我真係唔想男朋友似我細佬咁要我照顧囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6aa88eff59cf59a9c4853544614619d49a1c09c5","tid":923782,"uid":129573,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T14:05:56.000Z","msg":"你自己睇樣先咋wor<br />\n食得咸魚抵得渴"},{"pid":"ef43b1102d92cc76ced87935122a95a1c0715c2c","tid":923782,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T14:31:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbe8e43adb92d8c519b2cf4b832bc11b26a6a425","tid":923782,"uid":216992,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T14:35:15.000Z","msg":"On99"},{"pid":"d5602696d66fe2dc1190dd9f75e556ac585b5742","tid":923782,"uid":154106,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T14:35:38.000Z","msg":"你可以做大哥哥啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7795e58caad870a219ee8b0e7d943b23333cb4b","tid":923782,"uid":38904,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":